--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This role manages netsniff_ng.

The netsniff-ng toolkit currently consists of the following utilities:
 - netsniff-ng: the zero-copy sniffer, pcap capturer and replayer itself.
 - trafgen: a high performance zero-copy network packet generator.
 - astraceroute: an autonomous system (AS) and geo-ip trace route utility.
 - ifpps: a top-like kernel networking and system statistics tool.
 - bpfc: a tiny Berkeley Packet Filter compiler supporting Linux extensions.

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: netsniff_ng
       netsniff_ng_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: netsniff_ng
       netsniff_ng_state: 'remove'

INACTIVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: netsniff_ng
       netsniff_ng_state: 'inactive'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VARIABLES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  netsniff_ng_state
    Description: Control the state of the role.
    Implemented: 0.1
    Required   : False
    Value      : Predetermined
    Type       : String
    Default    : 'install'
    Options    :
      Install : 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
      Remove  : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'
      Inactive: 'quiesce' | 'inactive'

